{"tid":12241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"林祖舜：有人有組織打散高登 情況嚴重過鎅票","createTime":"2016-11-29T14:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T03:28:11.000Z","uid":39233,"like":1,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"584f91fcd695606f158f32001dfcc81c40057f08","tid":12241,"uid":39233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:44:36.000Z","msg":"【新增內容】不少高登用戶過檔新成立「LIHKG討論區」，令行政總裁林祖舜非常頭痕。他接受本報訪問時指，認為今次事件是有人有組織地，希望分化、打散香港一個有極高凝聚力的平台，「情況嚴重過鎅票。」<br />\n<br />\n他表示，有人虛構前員工身入，去發散一些，他將要下台，以及iPhone上唔到高登官方App等不盡不實、抹黑的消息，認為「情況唔似係一個普通寫App人做」。<br />\n<br />\n你表示，「好難估係咩人做，但純睇目的就係分化高登。你話邊啲人想分化高登？我諗都應該唔少人，有啲人覺得高登係幾自由嘅平台，好多人喺度暢所欲言，你知好多人又唔係好鍾意啲咁自由嘅氣氛。」他認為，有人希望打散高登。被問到是否「鎅票」概念，他指，「我覺得嚴重過鎅票。」他指出，高登一向出名有凝聚力，如果被打散，再難以聚集同一股力量。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，公司沒有派打手到「LIHKG討論區」呼籲會員回歸高登。被問到何以封殺於高登宣傳LIHKG用戶，他表示高登一向不容宣傳商業品牌，「條界線冇變過」。<br />\n<br />\n高登官方應用反應慢，他表示，「我哋有時都錄得不尋常流量，咁可能因為我哋出名啲，要封都封我哋先，不過食得咸魚抵得渴。」他又指，已向蘋果提交新iOS版本App，希望速度上有所改善，會繼續做好高登，令會員回歸，但現階段不會再批第三方應用，「見過鬼怕黑」。<br />\n<br />\n高登最新發聲明，指有人再以「禿伯」之名，假扮高登前職員發表失實言論聲明，指對於該名人士所發表的誹謗言論，保留追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n掌握財經地產資訊，即Like「蘋果ATM」fb專頁啦！<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyatm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyatm&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=4c344c23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyatm</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161129&amp;guid=55981789&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161129%26guid%3D55981789%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&d=MAn3riz0%2FQ%2FS8BFDrurXlZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=c4100559\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161129%26guid%3D55981789%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant&h=6ccf737b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161129&amp;guid=55981789&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant</a>轉自蘋果"},{"pid":"f9fada482295a342526c60c125b7d0dced3e295d","tid":12241,"uid":39233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:45:33.000Z","msg":"早洩唔抵得lihkg，開口出口術喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a214d1a36e7bba116d0ecf4b140b8ec95371b9f","tid":12241,"uid":39233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83ae757fb1f532b735fdf4abc3e7ef2b537664d","tid":12241,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:46:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早洩唔抵得lihkg，開口出口術喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8998fdba07927ed7b2588903380cd51b6f8ba723","tid":12241,"uid":39233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:47:51.000Z","msg":"冇人覆既，究竟呢到係咪冇人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c5eba160701f5b7a7c1bbe874dd6cdeabd7d79","tid":12241,"uid":16414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:47:52.000Z","msg":"正宗垂死掙扎"},{"pid":"1d3347e9d7f7438fb8cb9bdeb4e2c1010259b980","tid":12241,"uid":3128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:48:57.000Z","msg":"林狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ab37f19ae2d45a7b7746dd4ceff7b653890bfb","tid":12241,"uid":39233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:50:04.000Z","msg":"我係佢我會唔抵得老母先，重好生意過自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e0b6fffe4e391051b4b811fb2688aa16e120f8","tid":12241,"uid":30940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:51:28.000Z","msg":"叫佢食屎啦<br />\n自己垃圾就屈鳩人抹黑<br />\n極度無恥"},{"pid":"ca93622cb6beef872d65270d86bfb1aef527f86d","tid":12241,"uid":39233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:51:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2333e94f826d98f3d2e6b49377097802d27dfb","tid":12241,"uid":20631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:52:50.000Z","msg":"輸打贏要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829effb1631b8e513b6bd9a5130c1e948415d59f","tid":12241,"uid":28704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:52:55.000Z","msg":"傻尻早洩"},{"pid":"0f3d39ab3754d705fcc8cbe7306ca991725ad651","tid":12241,"uid":6870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:52:57.000Z","msg":"之前搞鳩lihk果時又冇咁多野講，林早洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46bd38455f633d87ef380ff49824681861ea1bb0","tid":12241,"uid":26846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:53:55.000Z","msg":"同民主黨一樣"},{"pid":"5eab04633a377dee7e46bb6e53a54871151536a6","tid":12241,"uid":39233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:54:06.000Z","msg":"高登近日封殺高登第三方手機App「HKG+」，致群情洶湧，更令不少高登用戶過檔新成立「LIHKG討論區」。LIHKG上周五蘋果App Store上架後，旋即成為下載榜首；今日LIHKG亦已喺Android Play Store上架，LIHKG官方表示，網頁版也會稍後推出。<br />\n<br />\n高登行政總裁林祖舜，就事件接受本報訪問，他表示高登流量未見受影響，每日Page view維持約600萬。對於有人於「LIHKG討論區」指他將被拉下台，連CEO都冇得做，他表示，「<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我依家就係話畀大家聽，我仍然有做！（屹立不倒？）暫時都屹立不倒！</span></span>」<br />\n<br />\n他向本報指出，當年予「HKG+」作為第三方手機App，已訂立條款，包括「HKG+」不得暫存網頁內容，以及不可自行賣廣告。不過「HKG+」早於超過半年前已被發現違反承諾，其後高登已向其作警告。至一個月前，「HKG+」再被發現私自暫存網頁內容，「你都知我哋成日收律師信，變咗有啲人以為佢係我哋，封信就畀咗我哋。因為佢哋暫存我哋啲內容，我哋鏟咗就喺佢度出現返。」因此決定停止與「HKG+」合作。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，當時「HKG+」表示希望予一個月時間寬限，以向付費VIP用戶負責，「完全冇估到，原來呢個時間係籌備呢樣嘢（LIHKG）。」"},{"pid":"286419095c282800032d597aa1afba6eb745a25e","tid":12241,"uid":4412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:54:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前搞鳩lihk果時又冇咁多野講，林早洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪臭係"},{"pid":"7c056a32e4d5098ec39dc309591814633b3dc283","tid":12241,"uid":39233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T14:55:26.000Z","msg":"做咩負皮我，我都係照copy姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d9b27193d70c86937e2b62438fb1b0f19627b8","tid":12241,"uid":7375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d78d9f8e0db81635dbdac1d28d35978e7a7e9f04","tid":12241,"uid":10441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"D票你架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a9578ed82ffdd9361622beee9750cfe87b05c1e","tid":12241,"uid":608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:04:48.000Z","msg":"之前又話唔介意年輕人開新討論區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ceb9ec40ff248573e69bbaa87416a9cc68069f","tid":12241,"uid":39263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:06:01.000Z","msg":"屹立不倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ca827a49bbef17e80351576afec60d8924e096","tid":12241,"uid":10438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:07:49.000Z","msg":"食屎狗早洩"},{"pid":"3772db74596411f4df1c4e6bc40656d94c152695","tid":12241,"uid":9601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T15:10:39.000Z","msg":"隻狗見住啲錢係咁流走依家驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" cl